# Code Blocks

## Inline Code

You can use `inline code` for small code snippets.

## Code Blocks

```php
namespace App\Models;

class User extends Model
{
    protected $fillable = ['name', 'email'];

    public function posts()
    {
        return $this->hasMany(Post::class);
    }
}
```

